### Admin endpoint without token should fail with 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/dashboard

### Admin endpoint with USER token should fail with 403
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Admin endpoint with ADMIN token should work
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

